- Have you ever been to Michigan, Wally?
- I went to Detroit for a meeting.

01:05:00.429 --> 01:05:02.454
Oh.
I'm talking about the upper peninsula.

01:05:02.598 --> 01:05:04.532
I've got a little cabin there
on Neebish Island.

01:05:04.667 --> 01:05:06.897
Been in the family for 30 years.

01:05:07.036 --> 01:05:10.335
I'm thinking of taking Kassie there.
I know it's early, but I'm really feeling it.

01:05:10.473 --> 01:05:12.907
I mean, what do you think?
You want another beer?

01:05:13.275 --> 01:05:14.469
No, no, no, thank you.

01:05:14.610 --> 01:05:17.204
- You sure?
- Yeah, and I do have to go.

01:05:17.346 --> 01:05:21.510
Uh, you know, hey, listen,
I'm so happy, uh, that we did this.

01:05:21.650 --> 01:05:23.174
The kid hates me, Wally.

01:05:24.854 --> 01:05:29.655
No, no, no.
No, I don't think, uh, Sebastian hates you.

01:05:29.792 --> 01:05:32.386
No, no, he does.
He's told me a couple times.

01:05:32.728 --> 01:05:34.525
Oh, well, um...

01:05:35.264 --> 01:05:38.495
It's just, oh, man, he's got some, uh...

01:05:39.668 --> 01:05:41.863
- Rough edges?
- Yeah, that's it, yeah. I mean, he's...

01:05:42.004 --> 01:05:45.838
He worries a lot, he questions everything.
He's really...

01:05:45.975 --> 01:05:48.170
- Neurotic?
- Yes, that's the word.

01:05:48.310 --> 01:05:50.107
So, what's the problem?

01:05:51.347 --> 01:05:53.679
Well, I don't really relate to that.

01:05:53.816 --> 01:05:55.147
Well...

01:05:58.053 --> 01:06:01.784
Neurotic is simply an intense form
